            "body": {
                "value": "<hr class=\"style-mint\" />\r\n<p class=\"text-align-center\">View online resume and <strong>recent</strong> work portfolio&nbsp;here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://kimberly-domenick.netlify.app/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://kimberly-domenick.netlify.app</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"style-mint\" />\r\n<p>This portfolio showcases <strong>older</strong> <strong>front-end</strong> and <strong>Drupal </strong>development work from 2018 and earlier.&nbsp; &nbsp;Some sites and projects live behind a firewall, and are&nbsp;<strong>not accessible to the public</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
