            "body": {
                "value": "<p>My Creative Portfolio is <strong>more Pinterest than Picasso</strong>, but it's how I prefer to spend my free time: painting, crafting, making jewelry, decorating and generally being creative.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See the Interiors photos below and <a href=\"/blog/bargain-staging\">this article</a> for info on what I call 'Bargain Staging,' the art of staging your home for resale, and doing minor renovations, while on a limited budget.</p>\r\n",
