            },
            "path": {
                "alias": "/about",
                "pid": "45",
                "langcode": "en"
            },
            "menu_link": [],
            "body": {
                "value": "<p><span><span><span>I live in South-Central Pennsylvania, but I work remotely as a UX Engineer for a web development agency.&nbsp; I’ve been in the IT field for over 20 years in various roles but with a focus on front-end development and UX/UI for web applications and content management systems.&nbsp; In recent years, I’ve also put my skills to use in my community volunteering as a web master for two non-profits.&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span><span>My favorite part of web development is working with Drupal, and I enjoy documenting my experiences (both good and bad!) in my <a href=\"/blog\">Blog</a>.&nbsp; I'm a member of the Drupal&nbsp;<br />\r\nAssociation and an <a href=\"https://www.acquia.com/customer-success/learning-services/acquia-certification-program\">Acquia Certified Site Builder for Drupal 8</a>.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span><span>Outside of the office, I put on my artistic hat and/or my DIY hat and busy myself with everything from minor home renovations to art and crafts, painting, jewelry making, wine-making, and anything that allows me to be creative.&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span><span>I love sci-fi, craft beer, the Pittsburgh Steelers, coffee, extra-large handbags, and Android OS.&nbsp; I like my steak cooked to medium, prefer driving over flying, and I’m equally as happy surrounded by noise and friends as I am sitting quietly on my front porch.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span><span>Whether it’s technical or creative, I’m passionate about doing things well and to the best of my ability, and this website is a tribute to that.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n",
                "summary": "",
                "format": "full_html"
            },
            "layout_builder__layout": {
                "section": {}
            }
        }
    },
